text: Number 111 is a 1919 Hungarian thriller movie directed by Alexander Korda and based on the novel by Jenő Heltai. It stars Gábor Rajnay, María Corda, Gyula Bartos and was distributed by Corvin Film. ==Other websites== * Category:1919 movies Category:Thriller movies Category:Hungarian silent movies Category:Movies directed by Alexander Korda
